data.description: Welcome to 9029 Black Cherry Trail! This 5 bedroom/3 bedroom home is located in the Pike Road school district. Functional open floor plan with designer features throughout including solid surface countertops, stainless appliances, LVP flooring, wood burning fireplace with gas lighter, custom cabinetry, and designer lighting and plumbing fixtures. The primary bedroom is large and offers dual vanities, separate shower and soaking tub, and walk in closets. On the opposite side of the primary bedroom, there are 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom. On the second floor there are additional 2 bedrooms and a full bath. The exterior includes a two car garage with large additional storage, mature landscaping, and a covered and uncovered patio, all located on of the largest fully privacy fenced lots in the neighborhood. Call today for a personal tour!
